== Historic site ==  
=== National Historic site ===  
* Nishinorikura Kofun (part of the "Somanouchi Kofun Group") - Designated a National Historic site on February 13, 2018, as part of the expanded Historic site of the preexisting "Nishiyama Kofun" to include Nishinorikura Kofun and rename it to "Somanouchi Kofun Group."<ref>[http://www.bunka.go.jp/koho_hodo_oshirase/hodohappyo/1397922.html Regarding the designation1 of Historic sites, etc.] (Cultural Affairs Agency, Press Release, November 17, 2017).</ref><ref name="Notification">Ministry of Education, Culture, Sports, Science, and Technology Notification No. 19, February 13, 2018.</ref>  

